OL,4,CWorld's wealthiest 'at heart of climate
OL,5,Cproblem'
OL,6, The world's wealthy must radically
OL,7, change their lifestyles to tackle
OL,8, climate change, a report says.
OL,10,FIt says the world's wealthiest 1%
OL,11,Fproduce double the combined carbon
OL,12,Femissions of the poorest 50%, according
OL,13,Fto the UN.
OL,15,FThe wealthiest 5% alone - the so-called
OL,16,F"polluter elite" - contributed 37% of
OL,17,Femissions growth between 1990 and 2015.
OL,19,FThe authors want to deter SUV drivers
OL,20,Fand frequent fliers - and persuade the
OL,21,Fwealthy to insulate their homes well.
